Usage: VER [<nickname>]
  This command will send a CTCP VERSION to the given nickname or
  nicknames.  The remote client will reply with its version
  information.  Do not use with too long a list of nicknames or
  server flood control will kick in and the return times will be
  inaccurate.

  If no nickname is given, the query is sent to the current
  channel.

See Also:
  CTCP
